Cantrips			KEY:Cantrips ~ Circle of the Oak			SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.DruidClassFeature.CircleOfTheOakFeature.SpecialQuality	DESC:You know the druidcraft and fire seeds cantrips, plus two other cantrips of your choice from the druid's cantrip list.
Nature's Prescience	KEY:Nature's Prescience ~ Circle of the Oak	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.DruidClassFeature.CircleOfTheOakFeature.SpecialQuality	DESC:Your mastery over your spells is so great that you waste little magical energy. Once per day, you can recover one of your expended 1st---level spell slots during a short rest. Starting at 3rd level, you can use this feature twice per day, and one of the slots you recover can be 2nd level. Starting at 5th level, you can use this feature three times per day, and one of the slots you recover can be 3rd level.
Circle Spells		KEY:Circle Spells ~ Circle of the Oak		SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.DruidClassFeature.CircleOfTheOakFeature.SpecialQuality	DESC:You always have the following spells prepared, provided you are able to cast druid spells of the given level. They do not count against the number of spells you can prepare each day. If a circle spell does not appear on the druid spell list, the spell is, nonetheless, a druid spell for you. 1-Entangle, 2-Augury, 3-Call Lightning, 4-Divination, 5-Cone of Cold	SPELLKNOWN:CLASS|Druid=1|Entangle|Druid=2|Augury|Druid=3|Call Lightning|Druid=4|Divination|Druid=5|Cone of Cold

