Wide Arc				KEY:Wide Arc ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.DeathDealerSelection	DESC:If you are wielding a two-handed weapon, when you hit a creature with a melee attack you can spend one expertise die to sweep into another creature. Roll the expertise die and choose a creature within your reach. The chosen creature takes damage of the same type as the attack equal to your expertise die roll + your Strength modifier.
