Careful Attack			KEY:Careful Attack ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.Unerring Attacker Selection	DESC:When you make an attack roll, before you roll your attack you can spend one expertise die, roll it, and add the number rolled to the attack roll.
Glancing Blow			KEY:Glancing Blow ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.Unerring Attacker Selection	DESC:When you would miss with a melee attack, you can spend one expertise die; roll that die, and add the number rolled to the attack roll. If the new total would be a hit, the result is a glancing blow, not a true hit. The target takes half damage from the attack. The damage is of the weapon's damage type, but it delivers no additional effect associated with the weapon or the attack.
Nick					KEY:Nick ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.Unerring Attacker Selection	DESC:When you would miss with a ranged attack, you can spend one expertise die; roll that die, and add the number rolled to the attack roll. If the new total would be a hit, the result is a nick, not a true hit. The target takes half damage from the attack. The damage is of the weapon's damage type, but it delivers no additional effect associated with the weapon or the attack.
Shield Swipe			KEY:Shield Swipe ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.Unerring Attacker Selection	DESC:When you are wielding a shield and would miss with an opportunity attack, you can spend one expertise die, roll it, and add the number rolled as a bonus to that opportunity attack roll.
