Great Fortitude			KEY:Great Fortitude ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.UnstoppableSelection	DESC:When you make a Constitution saving throw, you can spend one expertise die, roll it, and add the number rolled as a bonus to your saving throw.
