Iron Will				KEY:Iron Will ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.UnstoppableSelection	DESC:When you make a Wisdom saving throw, you can spend one expertise die, roll it, and add the number rolled as a bonus to your saving throw.
Lightning Reflexes		KEY:Lightning Reflexes ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality.UnstoppableSelection	DESC:When you make a Dexterity saving throw, you can spend one expertise die, roll it, and add the number rolled as a bonus to your saving throw.
