Level 11: Combat Surge		KEY:Combat Surge ~ Fighter	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.FighterClassFeature.SpecialQuality	DESC:Your prowess allows you to execute a series of quick strikes that less trained warriors would have a hard time replicating. Benefit: Once per day, you can use a combat surge on your turn. During that turn, you can take a second action, and when you roll any expertise die, the number rolled is doubled. You cannot use another combat surge until you have completed a long rest. At 14th, 17th, and 20th level, the number of times per day that you can use a combat surge increases by one, but you can use only one per turn.

