Level 1: Mindful Defense		KEY:Mindful Defense ~ Monk	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeature.MonkClassFeature.SpecialQuality	DESC: You use intuition and your sense of your surroundings to protect yourself from harm. You move a moment before an enemy attacks or steel yourself before a spell affects you. Benefit: While you are wearing no armor and are not using a shield, your Armor Class equals 10 + your Dexterity modifier + your Wisdom modifier.
